uniface_104afv1665702535715.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/afv1665702535715.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/afv1665702535715.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"afv1665702535715\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Returns the text of the specified label.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"afv1665702535715__topic_d127280e1_d127281e1_d127282e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"afv1665702535715__p_d127283e1_d127284e1_d127285e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Return</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">LabelObject</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">.getValue()</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"afv1665702535715__section_w1240ab1b5b3_w1241ab1b5_w1242ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d961798e67\">Arguments </h2>\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"afv1665702535715__section_w1243ab1b5b5_w1244ab1b5_w1245ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d961798e76\">Return Value</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"afv1665702535715__parml_hhr_c3v_cwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">Return</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">Value of the field label represented by the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">uniface.Label</span>\n            object.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"afv1665702535715__section_w1246ab1b5b7_w1247ab1b5_w1248ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d961798e97\">Exceptions</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following exceptions may be thrown:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">uniface.InvalidDataObjectException</code></li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"afv1665702535715__section_yrv_gmv_1dc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d961798e114\">Example: Getting the Text of a Label </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"afv1665702535715__p_d127310e1_d127311e1_d127312e1\">A Label object can be obtained from an occurrence or\n        from a field, so the following statements are equivalent.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104afv1665702535715_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"afv1665702535715__codeblock_yzt_g3v_cwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vText = this.getEntity(\"ENT1\").getOccurrence(0).getField(\"NAME\").getLabel().getValue();\nvText = this.getEntity(\"ENT1\").getOccurrence(0).getLabel(\"NAME\").getValue();</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/shk1665703139073.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>uniface.InvalidDataObjectException</a><p>Exception thrown if the object on which the function is called is no longer valid.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525665\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525665\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "getValue() Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 14, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Returns the text of the specified label. Return = LabelObject .getValue() Arguments None Return Value Return Value of the field label represented by the uniface.Label object. Exceptions The following exceptions may be thrown: uniface.InvalidDataObjectException Example: Getting the Text of a Label A Label object can be obtained from an occurrence or from a field, so the following statements are equivalent. Explain this code vText = this.getEntity(\"ENT1\").getOccurrence(0).getField(\"NAME\").getLabel().getValue(); vText = this.getEntity(\"ENT1\").getOccurrence(0).getLabel(\"NAME\").getValue(); Copy Related Links uniface.InvalidDataObjectException Exception thrown if the object on which the function is called is no longer valid. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}